divs: Sighting Detailsi was in the car with my girlfriend and she told me to look out the window up over the horizon and we seen 3 orangey-red orbs the moved to form a triangle then they moved in different directions an disappered it was not any stars or anything i could explain,and bein an amature astronomer i can tell the difference between a star an a planet an i know when something should not be there.I am convinced that it was e.t. in origin.
